Package paint_overhaul.alerts

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutAlert
    Class to create an about alert for the application.
    HelpAlert
    This class creates the help menu from Help->Help Contents.
    LogAlert
    This class creates a window to read the log file while in the application.
    LossWarning
    This class creates a warning if a loss is going to occur when saving.
    ReleaseNotesAlert
    Class to create a release note alert.
    ResizeCanvasAlert
    Class to create an alert when resizing the canvas.
    SmartSaveAlert
    Creates the pop-up window for the smart save notification.
